<%- meta title: "Услуги"
    meta og: { title: "Услуги"} %>

      <main class="main">
        
        <section class="section section_first section_pad_large services-promo">
          <div class="section__wrp services-promo__wrp scene">
            <div class="section__header section__header_compensate services-promo__header">
              <h2 class="section__heading heading heading_type_h2 services-promo__heading">
                <span class="section__heading-text">Чем мы занимаемся</span>
              </h2>
            </div>
            
            <div class="section__body services-promo__body">
              <div class="services-promo__img">
                <div class="services-promo__img-wrp">
                  <img src="<%= asset_path 'services/promo/bg.svg' %>" alt="firm-style" class="services-promo__img-bg layer" data-depth="0.40">
                  <img src="<%= asset_path 'services/promo/icon2.svg' %>" alt="firm-style" class="services-promo__img-icon2 layer" data-depth="0.60">
                  <img src="<%= asset_path 'services/promo/icon.svg' %>" alt="firm-style" class="services-promo__img-icon layer" data-depth="0.80">
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="services-promo__caption caption caption_size_l">
                Мы&nbsp;делаем это реально круто
              </div>
              
              <a href="#services" class="services-promo__link js-anchor-link">
                <span class="services-promo__link-icon">
                  <svg
                      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                      xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
                      width="20px" height="11px">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                      d="M19.435,1.707 L10.707,10.435 C10.317,10.825 9.683,10.825 9.293,10.435 L0.565,1.707 C0.174,1.316 0.174,0.683 0.565,0.293 C0.955,-0.098 1.589,-0.098 1.979,0.293 L10.000,8.313 L18.021,0.293 C18.411,-0.098 19.044,-0.098 19.435,0.293 C19.825,0.683 19.825,1.316 19.435,1.707 Z"/>
                </svg>
                </span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        
        <section id="services" class="section section_pad_medium section_green_light services">
          <div class="section__wrp services__wrp">
            <div class="section__body services__body">
              <div class="services__icon-col icon-col icon-col_main icon-col_border">
                <div class="icon-col__list icon-col__list_grid-two">
                  <div class="icon-col__item services__item js-animation js-animation_fadeInLeft" data-animation-delay="0">
                    <div class="icon-col__img-wrp js-tilter">
                      <img src="<%= asset_path 'services/icons/1.svg' %>" alt="services" class="icon-col__img tilter__figure">
                      <img src="<%= asset_path 'services/icons/1_bg.svg' %>" alt="services" class="icon-col__bg">
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="icon-col__text">
                      <div class="icon-col__title heading heading_type_h4">
                        Интернет-магазины
                      </div>
                      
                      <div class="icon-col__caption caption caption_size_g">
                        Помогаем продавать ваши товары. <br class="md-show xs-hide"/>В&nbsp;нашем портфолио уже несколько <br class="md-show xs-hide"/>десятков успешных историй.
                      </div>
                      
                      <a href="<%= ecom_path %>" class="icon-col__button button button_theme_border button_size_g">
                        Подробнее
                      </a>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="icon-col__item services__item js-animation js-animation_fadeInRight" data-animation-delay="100ms">
                    <div class="icon-col__img-wrp js-tilter">
                      <img src="<%= asset_path 'services/icons/2.svg' %>" alt="services" class="icon-col__img tilter__figure">
                      <img src="<%= asset_path 'services/icons/2_bg.svg' %>" alt="services" class="icon-col__bg">
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="icon-col__text">
                      <div class="icon-col__title heading heading_type_h4">
                        Сложные решения
                      </div>
                      
                      <div class="icon-col__caption caption caption_size_g">
                        Затачиваем под ваш бизнес CRM, ERP, системы отчетности и&nbsp;другие продукты. Чем сложнее, тем интереснее.
                      </div>
                      
                      <a href="<%= custom_development_path %>"
                          class="icon-col__button button button_theme_border button_size_g">
                        Подробнее
                      </a>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="icon-col__item services__item js-animation js-animation_fadeInRight" data-animation-delay="100ms">
                    <div class="icon-col__img-wrp js-tilter">
                      <img src="<%= asset_path 'services/icons/3.svg' %>" alt="services" class="icon-col__img tilter__figure">
                      <img src="<%= asset_path 'services/icons/3_bg.svg' %>" alt="services" class="icon-col__bg">
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="icon-col__text">
                      <div class="icon-col__title heading heading_type_h4">
                        Поддержка и развитие
                      </div>
                      
                      <div class="icon-col__caption caption caption_size_g">
                        Мы&nbsp;любим долгосрочные отношения и&nbsp;после запуска помогаем вашему продукту эволюционировать и&nbsp;идти в&nbsp;ногу с&nbsp;технологиями.
                      </div>
                      
                      <a href="<%= support_path %>"
                          class="icon-col__button button button_theme_border button_size_g">
                        Подробнее
                      </a>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="icon-col__item services__item js-animation js-animation_fadeInLeft" data-animation-delay="200ms">
                    <div class="icon-col__img-wrp js-tilter">
                      <img src="<%= asset_path 'services/icons/4.svg' %>" alt="services" class="icon-col__img tilter__figure">
                      <img src="<%= asset_path 'services/icons/4_bg.svg' %>" alt="services" class="icon-col__bg">
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="icon-col__text">
                      <div class="icon-col__title heading heading_type_h4">
                        Мобильные приложения
                      </div>
                      
                      <div class="icon-col__caption caption caption_size_g">
                        Для сайта на&nbsp;<nobr>1С-Битрикс</nobr> сделаем мобильное приложение по&nbsp;ошеломляющей цене. Мы&nbsp;даже выступаем с&nbsp;докладами об&nbsp;этом.
                      </div>
                      
                      <a href="<%= mobile_path %>"
                          class="icon-col__button button button_theme_border button_size_g">
                        Подробнее
                      </a>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="icon-col__item services__item js-animation js-animation_fadeInLeft" data-animation-delay="100ms">
                    <div class="icon-col__img-wrp js-tilter">
                      <img src="<%= asset_path 'services/icons/5.svg' %>" alt="services" class="icon-col__img tilter__figure">
                      <img src="<%= asset_path 'services/icons/5_bg.svg' %>" alt="services" class="icon-col__bg">
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="icon-col__text">
                      <div class="icon-col__title heading heading_type_h4">
                        Корпоративные сайты
                      </div>
                      
                      <div class="icon-col__caption caption caption_size_g">
                        Мы&nbsp;любим долгосрочные отношения, ежедневная поддержка и&nbsp;развитие проекта также важны, <br class="xs-hide"/>
                        как и&nbsp;сама разработка.
                      </div>
                      
                      <a href="<%= website_path %>"
                          class="icon-col__button button button_theme_border button_size_g">
                        Подробнее
                      </a>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="icon-col__item services__item js-animation js-animation_fadeInRight" data-animation-delay="200ms">
                    <div class="icon-col__img-wrp js-tilter">
                      <img src="<%= asset_path 'services/icons/6.svg' %>" alt="services" class="icon-col__img tilter__figure">
                      <img src="<%= asset_path 'services/icons/6_bg.svg' %>" alt="services" class="icon-col__bg">
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="icon-col__text">
                      <div class="icon-col__title heading heading_type_h4">
                        Привлечение клиентов
                      </div>
                      
                      <div class="icon-col__caption caption caption_size_g">
                        Собираем лиды, работаем с&nbsp;узнаваемостью бренда и&nbsp;лояльностью клиента: ведем социальные сети, настраиваем контекстную и&nbsp;медийную рекламу.
                      </div>
                      
                      <a href="<%= clients_path %>"
